"Eh, you got a wrong number, dino-boy," Jackie tells him.  "I'm a 
descendant of the original, not the real McCoy."

--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, foxmanroar1@a... wrote:
> Convoy looked back at Kup and Ygg, but he could not understand why 
they were 
> ignoring him. Suddenly he felt a slight tremble and soon the 
trembling became 
> a punding, which then became a booming like thunder... He slowly 
turned to see 
> a gigantic pair of teeth reflecting his own face back at him, 
startled he 
> fell backwards as grimlock in his new form roared loud enough to 
send a ripple 
> through the sheild... The dino looked over the bots until his eyes 
fell on 
> Jackie... He transformed and placed a hand against the sheild. In 
his robot form 
> his chest and head looked the same as the old dino-bot, but 
everything else had 
> been updated, hydrolics, and muscle like cables intertwined around 
parts of 
> his arms and the rex's tail was stiff and lance like in his 
hand. "WheelJack?" 
> The bot looked at him, but shook his head and transformed back into 
the Dino 
> and lowered himself growling to their eye level. "Leave... or you 
will be 
> destroyed."
